### Duplicate response rotation
GET /rotation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "behavior": "duplicate method and URL responses rotate in file order"
}

### Default Strategy 1
GET /default
Content-Type: application/json

{ "n":  1 }

### Default Strategy 2
GET /default
Content-Type: application/json

{ "n":  2 }

### Status variant
# $status=202
GET /status-variant
Content-Type: application/json

{ "accepted": true }
